Name: ALL ACTIVEWEAR
Description:
This bra is perfect for every workout of your choice, from spin class to boxing. It comes in a classic scoop neck cut and a racerback design for style, support and performance. The racerback design offers tremendous support when you’re moving around and the moisture wicking fabric gives you a dry and cool feeling, no matter how sweaty the class. This sports bra is antimicrobial, moisture-wicking, and breathable as well.
Top comes with removable cups for extra customization.
The leggings? All the elements for perfection are here. The solid color-blocking in our ultimate performance compression fabric, have four-way stretch, the moisture wicking fabric, this design keeps everything where it should be.Adding to that, there’s also a hidden waistband pocket to store your tiniest essentials. These leggings are made for a goddess like you.
 
All our fabrics have the following features for maximal comfort and performance :
Moisture Wicking & BreathableShrink & Fade ResistantAnti-Pill4-way stretchAnti-Microbial
All KHONGBOON gear contains NFC technology, that allows you to connect to your mobile and enjoy exclusive content. *Model is wearing a Small Top & Bottom
Keywords: ACTIVITY, BOTTOMS, CROP TOPS, KITS, KITS + SETS, LEGGINGS, REMOVABLE PADDING, RUN, SPORTS BRAS, TOPS, TRAINING, VIEW ALL, YOGA

This bra is perfect for every workout of your choice, from spin class to boxing. It comes in a classic scoop neck cut and a racerback design for style, support and performance. The racerback design offers tremendous support when you’re moving around and the moisture wicking fabric gives you a dry and cool feeling, no matter how sweaty the class. This sports bra is antimicrobial, moisture-wicking, and breathable as well.
Top comes with removable cups for extra customization.
The leggings? All the elements for perfection are here. The solid color-blocking in our ultimate performance compression fabric, have four-way stretch, the moisture wicking fabric, this design keeps everything where it should be.Adding to that, there’s also a hidden waistband pocket to store your tiniest essentials. These leggings are made for a goddess like you.
 
All our fabrics have the following features for maximal comfort and performance :
Moisture Wicking & BreathableShrink & Fade ResistantAnti-Pill4-way stretchAnti-Microbial
All KHONGBOON gear contains NFC technology, that allows you to connect to your mobile and enjoy exclusive content. *Model is wearing a Small Top & Bottom
Keywords: ACTIVITY, BOTTOMS, CROP TOPS, KITS, KITS + SETS, LEGGINGS, REMOVABLE PADDING, RUN, SPORTS BRAS, TOPS, TRAINING, VIEW ALL, YOGA

Name: ALL ACTIVEWEAR
Description:
This bra is perfect for every workout of your choice, from spin class to boxing. It comes in a classic scoop neck cut and a racerback design for style, support and performance. The racerback design offers tremendous support when you’re moving around and the moisture wicking fabric gives you a dry and cool feeling, no matter how sweaty the class. This sports bra is antimicrobial, moisture-wicking, and breathable as well.
Top comes with removable cups for extra customization.
The leggings? All the elements for perfection are here. The solid color-blocking in our ultimate performance compression fabric, have four-way stretch, the moisture wicking fabric, this design keeps everything where it should be.Adding to that, there’s also a hidden waistband pocket to store your tiniest essentials. These leggings are made for a goddess like you.

This bra is perfect for every workout that might strike your fancy in its solid matching colors, from spin class to boxing. It comes in a classic scoop neck cut and a racerback design for style, support and performance. The racerback design offers tremendous support when you’re moving around and the moisture wicking fabric gives you a dry and cool feeling, no matter how sweaty the class. This sports bra is antimicrobial, moisture-wicking, and breathable. Top comes with removable cups for extra customization.
Leggings? Oh Yes! Hot studios and hard classes, you name it. These leggings in our ultimate performance compression fabric sculpts and lifts like no other.Breathable, 4-way stretch and sweat wicking make them ideal for every kind of sweat sesh you might find. Contrast seaming and panels flatter and elongate the silhouette.Did we also mention they include a tummy-flattening waistband and hidden waistband pocket to store your tiniest essentials?
All our fabrics have the following features for maximal comfort and performance :
Moisture Wicking & BreathableShrink & Fade ResistantAnti-Pill4-way stretchAnti-Microbial
All KHONGBOON gear contains NFC technology, that allows you to connect to your mobile and enjoy exclusive content. *Model is wearing a Small Top & Bottom
Keywords: ACTIVITY, BOTTOMS, KITS, KITS + SETS, LEGGINGS, REMOVABLE PADDING, RUN, SPORTS BRAS, TOPS, TRAINING, VIEW ALL, YOGA

Cute & stylish at the same time? You just found it. This sports bra is designed in our ultimate compression fabric with a birds eye mesh layer on-top. This lightweight design features soft shoulder straps, racerback with mesh layout and offers superb breathability and style.Quick-drying, moisture-wicking and four-way stretch is also provided.
The solid color blocked capris comes in our ultimate performance compression fabric, providing the best in performance and technology while using birds eye mesh inserts for optimal ventilation for those hot summer day workouts. Quick-drying, moisture-wicking, these leggings has four-way stretch for maximum performance. Store essentials in a hidden waistband pocket for convenience on-the-go.
All our fabrics have the following features for maximal comfort and performance:
Moisture Wicking & BreathableShrink & Fade ResistantAnti-Pill4-way stretchAnti-Microbial
All KHONGBOON gear contains NFC technology, that allows you to connect to your mobile and enjoy exclusive content. *Model is wearing a Small Top & Bottom
Keywords: ACTIVITY, BOTTOMS, CAPRIS, CROP TOPS, KITS, KITS + SETS, REMOVABLE PADDING, RUN, SPORTS BRAS, TOPS, TRAINING, VIEW ALL, YOGA

This sports bra is designed in our layered ultimate compression fabric for maximum bust support. The open back design offers ventilation and breathability, while the gold hook in back close back for a perfect fit. Stay cool wearing this versatile crop to a HIIT workout or a steamy hot yoga class.
Top comes with removable cups for extra customization.
All our fabrics have the following features for maximal comfort and performance :
Moisture Wicking & BreathableShrink & Fade ResistantAnti-Pill4-way stretch
All KHONGBOON gear contains NFC technology, that allows you to connect to your mobile and enjoy exclusive content.*Model is wearing a Small Top
